node.text: This is from last year when we were blessed with the opportunity to rebuild Jose Caballero’s truck after he and his family were harassed by a group of idiots during a camping trip. This moment was when we revealed to him the brand new camp trailer and Polaris General that we were able to give him along with his truck upgrades. This is still one of the coolest things I’ve ever been blessed to be part of 💯

node.text: Tomorrow we will tackle one of the most challenging recoveries of my career 😅 This 100,000 lb excavator has been stuck in this swamp for 12 weeks now….the owner finally ran out of options and decided to call us to the rescue. Most people see a photo like this and get instant anxiety but when I see pics like this I am filled with intense joy and excitement 🥰 Stay tuned for the video cause this one is bound to get western 🤠 @sanyamerica @kraftsmantrailers @yankum_ropes

node.text: This dude right here is my right and left hand and today we celebrate his birthday. @hans_smco is one of the scrappiest, most dedicated, and driven guys you’ll ever meet. He works circles around most people yet still finds time to be an excellent dad and husband. His loyalty and work ethic are unmatched and I’m grateful to have him in my corner…happy birthday, Pigeon! @hans_smco
